data.title: About: Lene Lai
data.meta_description: Lene Lai (Chinese: 賴琳恩; pinyin: Lài Lín'ēn; born 6 June 1989) is a Taiwanese actress and model. She was the 2nd runner-up of the Miss Asia Pageant 2008.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

Lene Lai (Chinese: 賴琳恩; pinyin: Lài Lín'ēn; born 6 June 1989) is a Taiwanese actress and model. She was the 2nd runner-up of the Miss Asia Pageant 2008. (en)

Lene Lai (caratteri cinesi: 賴琳恩; pinyin: Lai Linen; Taipei, 6 giugno 1989) è un'attrice e modella taiwanese, conosciuta soprattutto per essere arrivata seconda al concorso di bellezza Miss Asia Pageant 2008. (it)

라이린언(중국어: 賴琳恩, 병음: Lài Lín'ēn, 한자음: 뢰림은, 1989년 6월 6일 ~ )은 중화민국의 배우, 모델이다. 타이베이시에서 태어났다. (ko)

賴琳恩 台灣演員，演出多部戲劇作品。2008年參加香港亞洲小姐競賽獲得季軍，進而知名度大開。 (zh)
